<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <title>Weekly Digest - Max Ischenko</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<!-- Eliminate all default margins -->
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222; text-align: left;">

  <div style="font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin: 1rem 0;">
    {{#if someone_special}}
    –ü—Ä–∏–≤—ñ—Ç, —Å–æ–Ω–µ—á–∫–æ!

    –¶–µ–π –¥–∞–π–¥–∂–µ—Å—Ç —Å–ø–µ—Ü—ñ–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ –¥–ª—è —Ç–µ–±–µ :-*
    <br><br>
    {{else}}
     –î–∞–π–¥–∂–µ—Å—Ç –±–ª–æ–≥–∞ <a
      href="https://maxua.com/">maxua.com</a> –∑–∞ {{dateFormatted}}. Enjoy
    &amp; share with others! 
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <!-- Wrap entire content in table with zero margins -->
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="left" valign="top" style="padding: 0;">
        <!-- Main content container with proper padding -->
        <div style="max-width: 620px; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
          
          {{#if posts.length}}
            {{#each posts}}
            <!-- Post Card -->
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0; padding: 0;">
              <tr>
                <td align="left" valign="top" style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.25rem; text-align: left;">
                  
                  <!-- Post Content -->
                  <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; text-align: left;">
                    <a href="https://maxua.com/p/{{this.id}}" style="color: #222; text-decoration: none; display: block; text-align: left;">{{{this.content_html}}}</a>
                  </div>
                  
                  <!-- Rich Link Preview -->
                  {{#if this.metadata.url}}
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem 0; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; background-color: white;">
                    <tr>
                      <!-- Image Column (conditionally shown) -->
                      {{#if this.metadata.image_url}}
                      <td width="30%" style="vertical-align: top; padding: 0;">
                        <div style="height: 120px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #f5f5f5;">
                          <a href="{{this.metadata.url}}" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; display: block;">
                            <img src="{{this.metadata.image_url}}" alt="Link preview" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;">
                          </a>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                      {{/if}}
                      
                      <!-- Text Content Column -->
                      <td style="vertical-align: top; padding: 0.5rem 1rem;">
                        <div style="min-width: 0; overflow: hidden;">
                          
                          {{#if this.metadata.title}}
                          <div style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #222; display: block; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">
                            <a href="{{this.metadata.url}}" target="_blank" style="color: #222; text-decoration: none;">{{this.metadata.title}}</a>
                          </div>
                          {{/if}}
                          
                          {{#if this.metadata.description}}
                          <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; max-height: 2.8em;">
                            {{this.metadata.description}}
                          </div>
                          {{/if}}
                          
                          <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777;">
                            <a href="{{this.metadata.url}}" target="_blank" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                              {{getDomain this.metadata.url}}
                            </a>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  {{/if}}
                  
                  <!-- Transistor.fm Podcast Embed -->
                  {{#if this.metadata.transistor_embed_code}}
                  <div style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                    <a href="https://share.transistor.fm/e/{{this.metadata.transistor_embed_code}}" target="_blank" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; display: block; padding: 12px; background-color: #f0f4f8; border: 1px solid #d0e0f0; border-radius: 8px;">
                      üéôÔ∏è Listen to this podcast episode (Startups Are Hard)
                    </a>
                    <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #555;">
                      Also available on: 
                      <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/startups-are-hard/id1616301447" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none;">Apple Podcast</a> | 
                      <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2lnCQcCqkCxRI8yVbNeJfm" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none;">Spotify</a> | 
                      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@maxua-public" style="color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none;">YouTube</a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  {{/if}}
                  
                  <!-- Post Meta -->
                  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 1rem 0 0 0; padding: 0;">
                    <tr>
                      <td align="left" valign="middle" style="text-align: left; color: #555; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                        <span style="display: inline-block; text-align: left;">{{this.formatted_date}}</span>
                      </td>
                      <td align="right" valign="middle" style="text-align: right; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                        <a href="https://maxua.com/p/{{this.id}}"
                          style="color: #222; text-decoration: underline;">Comment</a>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                  
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
            {{/each}}
          {{else}}
            <p style="color: #555; padding: 20px;">No new posts this week.</p>
          {{/if}}
          
          <!-- Footer -->
          <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px 5px 0 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #666; font-size: 13px; text-align: left;">
            <div style="text-align: left;">You're receiving this email
              because you subscribed to updates from Max Ischenko. Yes, you
              did.&nbsp;:) </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; text-align: left;">
              <a href="%%unsubscribeUrl%%" style="color: #999;
                text-decoration: none; text-align: left;">Click here</a> to unsubscribe.
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
